</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="98EBBA7182383ACA02ED2CE8D7040B43" pageId="null" pageNumber="386" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="253BCA090E622AD590507121C47ACDB7" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Mehlige Glockenblume</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="4C39B2DAA75A1595456760EE71413326" pageId="null" pageNumber="386" type="description">
<paragraph id="8F4FD65C3640B7BDF3899F83A05ACC5A" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="D4F0D278AFC3CB9969869C26C0DA9805" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Campanula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="386" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glomerata">
<emphasis id="66F81899FC54B4A01B9232C208FAE22E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">C. glomerata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 8) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="6B86DBB54687D573982AA9E7081E8932" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
Stengel und besonders Blattunterseiten dicht und kurz behaart; mittlere 
<normalizedToken id="1710BFBD0762068209277CAD89060F8D" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
bis 5 cm lang, 1
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="418ADF10A58F77C8DFA2ED4EAEECBA11" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">1/2</normalizedToken>
- 
<emphasis id="9BCCECD461A9644D505D7368314C9A53" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">3mal so lang wie breit;</emphasis>
Krone dunkelpurpurn. - 
<normalizedToken id="7DA6754F9729626375CAB72F7B74CD61" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="284C7FBA0E9BC7CEC3F5F1163E49671F" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
Sommer (
<normalizedToken id="63FF1F0D3B2C8D4EF9D733A5B3C37AC3" originalValue="später" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">spaeter</normalizedToken>
als 
<taxonomicName id="9322D1C3C2AF5935E2E65B946D037161" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Campanula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="386" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glomerata">
<emphasis id="B01EEAAE9CB1DCFE0ADE2049052A6783" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">C. glomerata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2ECB9F396A3D7E1EFD1D05687C319B26" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
<emphasis id="653BC1BD655D5674C80CBC0B4E780BAF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="F31CA0D06C7CF517446FD8C996C84DAC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">30:</emphasis>
Material aus Ungarn und 
<normalizedToken id="9A0CFEA53B42EC6B0F94A1B2AA053C68" originalValue="Rußland" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Russland</normalizedToken>
(Gadella 1964).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1CA395EDD78326B03EBF1DD2A4C9A3B7" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
<emphasis id="04FB2BD096532E87914B7DFB54953479" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan, seltener subalpin. Offene, steinige, trockene 
<normalizedToken id="A6FFC0E1E26D150C4E586CD2BF7016B0" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felsensteppen, lichte 
<normalizedToken id="4DD70D341A6B638B0A01D2634E093438" originalValue="Wälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Waelder</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="472415F9728892F4457A1DC845B5E77C" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
<emphasis id="69F65534C2E8D78C3C85358FD0EC11A2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="CA9E9E7E909BAB773A21C5FD4E18BC25" originalValue="Osteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Osteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="87D0A5F06CDD67317D66C257FDCD51C4" originalValue="Westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">Westwaerts</normalizedToken>
vereinzelt bis Westalpen und Mainzer Becken. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen, Wallis, Aostatal, 
<normalizedToken id="00BED092FB4162FF0EF594C572CF2B3F" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="386">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, Comerseegebiet, Val Camonica, Vintschgau. Aus Vorarlberg (bei Bludenz), von Sargans und aus dem Vorderrheintal (Cumbels-Peiden) ebenfalls angegeben.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
